rComments: Follow along with the lectures and ask questions, great prof who will teach you a lot.

Very knowledgeable professor in the area of solidworks and hand sketching. teaches at a good pace and will answer any question asked. is available outside class hours and is very helpful. MCG1100 is a heavy course with lots of lengthy assignments but jason taught efficient ways to speed up assignments

Jason heads the solidworks CAD section of the course. He's a great prof with a real understanding of design. Always available to answer any question and goes beyond course material to show useful features/techniques. He tends to go on a few tangents but they always relate to the course and are interesting usually related to his experience in design
